o-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 27, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104sdn1665703008210.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sdn1665703008210.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sdn1665703008210.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"sdn1665703008210\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $language\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"sdn1665703008210___language_272601\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return or set the current language code used for language-related global objects and language setups.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sdn1665703008210__p_d85421e1_d85422e1_d85423e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$language</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sdn1665703008210__p_d85424e1_d85425e1_d85426e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$language</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Language</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sdn1665703008210__p_d85427e1_d85428e1_d85429e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">$language = \"FR\"</code>\n</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sdn1665703008210__topic_d56732e1_d56733e1_d56734e1_d56735e1_d56736e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d948372e81\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"sdn1665703008210__table_d8990e1_d8991e1_d8992e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sdn1665703008210__table_d8990e1_d8991e1_d8992e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sdn1665703008210__table_d8990e1_d8991e1_d8992e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sdn1665703008210__table_d8990e1_d8991e1_d8992e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdn1665703008210__table_d8990e1_d8991e1_d8992e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Language</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdn1665703008210__table_d8990e1_d8991e1_d8992e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sdn1665703008210__table_d8990e1_d8991e1_d8992e1__entry__3\">\n Name of the desired language. It is recommended that you use the country codes from the ISO or ANSI standards.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sdn1665703008210__topic_d56737e1_d56738e1_d56739e1_d56740e1_d56741e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d948372e136\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sdn1665703008210__p_d85436e1_d85437e1_d85438e1\">Current language code.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sdn1665703008210__topic_d56742e1_d56743e1_d56744e1_d56745e1_d56746e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d948372e145\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sdn1665703008210__d6006e20\">Allowed in Form, Report, and Service components, but not in self-contained components.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sdn1665703008210__topic_d56747e1_d56748e1_d56749e1_d56750e1_d56751e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d948372e154\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sdn1665703008210__p_d85448e1_d85449e1_d85450e1\">Use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$language</span> to set or return the name of the current language.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sdn1665703008210__p_d85451e1_d85452e1_d85453e1\">If the language has not been set in an assignment file (with the setting <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$LANGUAGE</span> in <span class=\"ph filepath\">USYS:usys.asn</span> or your local assignment file), it defaults to USA. If you explicitly define a value for <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$language</span>, the assignment file setting is ignored.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sdn1665703008210__section_fph_slb_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d948372e178\">Example: Setting <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$language</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example saves the current language in general variable\n               $1, and sets the current language to German, which has a country code of DE:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"sdn1665703008210__pre_vkr_slb_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; save current language\n; set current language to German\n$1 = $language\n$language = \"DE\"\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sdn1665703008210__section_abw_plb_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d948372e195\">Example: Setting <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$language</span> and\n            <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$variation</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example shows how to correctly set\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$language</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$variation</span>. The example\n               assumes that you do not want to override any assignment file settings, but do want to\n               change the language and library if the defaults have been given.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"sdn1665703008210__pre_h33_qlb_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; trigger: apStart\nif ($language = \"USA\") ; default language used, so change to UK\n $language = \"UK\"\nendif ; otherwise, leave alone\nif ($variation = \"USYS\") ; default library used, so change to TECH_PUBS\n $variation = \"TECH_PUBS\"\nendif ; otherwise, leave alone\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">The only problem with the example (and the problem is unavoidable) is\n               that the assignment file below is ignored:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"sdn1665703008210__pre_i33_qlb_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$LANGUAGE = USA\n$VARIATION = USYS\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ead1665702665322.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>language</a><p>Specify the language used by the Sybase SQL Server for error messages.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oma1720015839839.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>display</a><p>Presents the form on the screen as display-only.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zbn1665702665252.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$keyboard</a><p>Return or set the current keyboard translation table.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/exe1665702665391.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$variation</a><p>Return or specify the name of the library containing objects needed by the application or component.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jcj1665702550017.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger apStart</a><p>System trigger that starts the application environment and controls the interaction of the application with the component manager.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dcg1665703007237.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$display</a><p>Return the name of the current display device translation table.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zum1665703230237.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$LANGUAGE</a><p>Specify the language to use for global objects and language setups.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531925\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531925\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$language Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 27, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $language Return or set the current language code used for language-related global objects and language setups. $language $language = Language Example: $language = \"FR\" Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Language String Name of the desired language. It is recommended that you use the country codes from the ISO or ANSI standards. Return Values Current language code. Use Allowed in Form, Report, and Service components, but not in self-contained components. Description Use $language to set or return the name of the current language. If the language has not been set in an assignment file (with the setting $LANGUAGE in USYS:usys.asn or your local assignment file), it defaults to USA. If you explicitly define a value for $language , the assignment file setting is ignored. Example: Setting $language The following example saves the current language in general variable $1, and sets the current language to German, which has a country code of DE: ; save current language ; set current language to German $1 = $language $language = \"DE\" Copy Example: Setting $language and $variation The following example shows how to correctly set $language and $variation . The example assumes that you do not want to override any assignment file settings, but do want to change the language and library if the defaults have been given. ; trigger: apStart if ($language = \"USA\") ; default language used, so change to UK $language = \"UK\" endif ; otherwise, leave alone if ($variation = \"USYS\") ; default library used, so change to TECH_PUBS $variation = \"TECH_PUBS\" endif ; otherwise, leave alone Copy The only problem with the example (and the problem is unavoidable) is that the assignment file below is ignored: $LANGUAGE = USA $VARIATION = USYS Copy Related Links language Specify the language used by the Sybase SQL Server for error messages. display Presents the form on the screen as display-only. $keyboard Return or set the current keyboard translation table. $variation Return or specify the name of the library containing objects needed by the application or component. trigger apStart System trigger that starts the application environment and controls the interaction of the application with the component manager. $display Return the name of the current display device translation table. $LANGUAGE Specify the language to use for global objects and language setups. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}